trans-unit.source: A collection of <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> objects.
trans-unit.target: Una colección de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" />.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> object contains <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> objects that represent user profiles from a data source.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> objeto contiene <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> objetos que representan los perfiles de usuario de un origen de datos.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> is returned from the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> methods of a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider>.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> se devuelve desde el <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, y <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> métodos de un <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider>.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> can be supplied to the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A> method to delete profile information and properties from the data source.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> pueden proporcionar a los <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A> método para eliminar la información de perfil y las propiedades del origen de datos.

trans-unit.source: The following code example allows a user to search for profiles using the <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A> and <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> methods.
trans-unit.target: En el ejemplo de código siguiente se permite que un usuario pueda buscar perfiles mediante el <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A> y <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> métodos.

trans-unit.source: The user can pass the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> returned by the `find` methods to the <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A> method to delete the associated profiles from the data source.
trans-unit.target: El usuario puede pasar la <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> devuelto por la `find` métodos para la <xref:System.Web.Profile.SqlProfileProvider.DeleteProfiles%2A> método para eliminar los perfiles asociados del origen de datos.

trans-unit.source: Creates a new, empty <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" />.
trans-unit.target: Crea un objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" /> nuevo vacío.

trans-unit.source: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> is constructed by profile provider implementers and returned from the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, and <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> methods of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> abstract class.
trans-unit.target: A <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> se construye mediante implementadores del proveedor del perfil y se devolvió desde el <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, y <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> métodos de la <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> clase abstracta.

trans-unit.source: For an example of a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> implementation that creates a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> for user profiles in a data store, see [Implementing a Profile Provider](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98).
trans-unit.target: Para obtener un ejemplo de un <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> implementación que crea una <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> para perfiles de usuario en un almacén de datos, vea [implementar un proveedor de perfil](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98).

trans-unit.source: A <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> object to add to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> que se va a agregar a la colección.

trans-unit.source: Adds the specified <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> object to the collection.
trans-unit.target: Agrega a la colección el objeto <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo" /> especificado.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.Add%2A> method is commonly used by profile-provider implementers to populate a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> to return from the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, or <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> method of the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> abstract class.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.Add%2A> método se usa normalmente por los implementadores de proveedor de perfiles para rellenar un <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> para devolver desde el <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.GetAllInactiveProfiles%2A>, <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindProfilesByUserName%2A>, o <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider.FindInactiveProfilesByUserName%2A> método de la <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> clase abstracta.

trans-unit.source: For an example of a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> implementation that creates a <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> for user profiles in a data store, see [Implementing a Profile Provider](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98).
trans-unit.target: Para obtener un ejemplo de un <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileProvider> implementación que crea una <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> para perfiles de usuario en un almacén de datos, vea [implementar un proveedor de perfil](http://msdn.microsoft.com/library/58de6e99-31a7-41b9-93ed-51b9b4a67e98).

trans-unit.target: Obtiene un valor que indica si la colección de información de perfil es segura para la ejecución de subprocesos.

trans-unit.target: Siempre es <see langword="false" />, ya que no se admiten colecciones de información de perfil seguras para la ejecución de subprocesos.

trans-unit.source: The collection is read-only.
trans-unit.target: La colección es de solo lectura.

trans-unit.source: Makes the contents of the <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" /> read-only.
trans-unit.target: Hace que el contenido de <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" /> sea de sólo lectura.

trans-unit.source: The <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> method marks the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> as read-only so that <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> objects cannot be added to or removed from the collection.
trans-unit.target: El <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> método marcas el <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> como de solo lectura para que <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfo> no se agregan o se quita de la colección de objetos.

trans-unit.source: After calling the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> method, you cannot change the <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> back to read/write.
trans-unit.target: Después de llamar a la <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection.SetReadOnly%2A> método, no se puede cambiar el <xref:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection> a lectura/escritura.

trans-unit.source: Gets the synchronization root.
trans-unit.target: Obtiene la raíz de sincronización.

trans-unit.source: Always <see langword="this" /> (<see langword="Me" /> in Visual Basic), because synchronization of <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" /> objects is not supported.
trans-unit.target: Es siempre <see langword="this" /> (<see langword="Me" /> en Visual Basic) porque no se admite la sincronización de objetos <see cref="T:System.Web.Profile.ProfileInfoCollection" />.
